      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable daily driver that's ready to get you where you need to go? This vehicle is in honest, fair condition and offers a solid, reliable performance that you can count on! While it shows some expected signs of wear and tear from its time on the road, it remains a practical and functional choice for anyone seeking a hardworking car at a great value. Come see why this sturdy ride is perfect for your next adventure!",
