    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional opportunity to own a vehicle in truly showroom condition. This motorcar has been meticulously preserved, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that retains its original factory freshness. Every mechanical component has been maintained to the highest standards, ensuring a driving experience that is indistinguishable from new. For the collector or driver who demands uncompromising quality and aesthetic perfection, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
